, delegator)).isEqualTo(42);\n        } finally {\n            Context.exit();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2451, "output": 875, "cacheRead": 15872, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19198, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780965198446, "responseId": "resp_0340217707820dcc016a275f4ec85c81909bf434a4ecf5652f"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_UqnTkCSWEkSFPe2mbU39B37Q|fc_0340217707820dcc016a275f5c16548190993646d87543b0aa", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1264 bytes to tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/java/org_mozilla/rhino/DelegatorTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780965215242}]}
